posting_body: ['THIS BEAUTIFUL SINGLE FAMILY HOUSE, TOTALLY RENOVATED, NEW FRESH PAINT, NEW WOOD FLOORING THROUGHOUT THE WHOLE HOUSE, NEW RENOVATED BATHROOMS, NEW KITCHEN WITH NEW APPLIANCES.', 'THIS HOUSE IS LOCATED IN THE HEART OF MIRAMAR.', '3BR + 2BA (GARAGE CONVERTED TO 4TH BEDROOM).', 'LARGE SPACES WITH HIGH CEILINGS.', 'GOOD BACKYARD GARDEN VERY GREEN AREA.', 'QUIET NEIGHBORHOOD.', 'CLOSE TO MALLS, NOT VERY FAR FROM BEACHES EASY ACCESS TO MAJOR HIGHWAYS.', "DON'T MISS IT.", 'PETS OK WITH LANDLORD APPROVAL.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE – NOT SHORT TERM.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 2.5 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
